item.title: "The fools in life want things fast and easy -money, success, attention." - Robert Greene You can't be an expert just like that. You can't build an empire overnight. You need to show prior results. Establish credibility. Actually build something. Battle tested. Most of all have patience. It just takes time! #entrepreneurship #startuplessons #grind #hustle #patience
